Okay, this map is called: mg_ninjas_trial. Its a Knife map, where you jump on platforms without jumping in the water, and trying to kill the other team. Theres a couple of very realistic traps, with physics, and all of that shit :D looks pretty good. like collapsing pillars and stuff.

But i hope you'll put this map into your servers, and PLEASE comment about if u can think of any changes, or if you find any bugs and stuff.
